libtableau is a library to support the Tableau(TM) forensic bridge (write blocker).

Project information:

* Status: experimental
* Licence: LGPL-3.0-or-later

For more information see:

* Project documentation: https://github.com/libyal/libtableau/wiki/Home
* How to build from source: https://github.com/libyal/libtableau/wiki/Building

